data.description: Nestled in a quiet community is this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom brick home boasting rooms with plenty of windows for natural light, gorgeous gray interior throughout, a screened-in back porch, walk in laundry room, and a large room which can be converted into a living room, great room, home gym, or home office; the possibilities are endless.  With a beautiful front porch, spacious front and back yards, and a 2 car carport, this home is perfect for family gatherings and so much more. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, restaurants, and the highway/interstate, this home awaits it's new homeowner. Seller will contribute towards closing costs.
